        "TerminalOutcome": {
          "description": "Distinct terminal outcomes a request can end in (P4.4, finding H12).\n\nBefore this taxonomy, an unavailable dataset (invalid/irrelevant generated\nSQL on a data-primary request) was answered with ``answer_conceptual`` \u2014\na plausible domain narrative that masked the data failure. These outcomes\nare now modeled separately so a data failure is reported as a data failure,\nnever as a conceptual success.",
          "enum": [
            "data_answer",
            "conceptual_answer",
            "evidence_unavailable",
            "clarification_required",
            "policy_blocked",
            "transient_failure"
          ],
